properties.Name: AminoAcidRelatedDatabase
properties.Description: The database(s) containing information and entries related to the amino acid.

Columns.Name: DatabaseId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a database.

Columns.Name: AminoAcidId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an amino acid.

Columns.Name: DatabaseEntry
Columns.Description:
The database entry of the associated type related to the amino acid.

Ex:
ModBase - P06968
SWISS2DPAGE - P06969
HAMAP - MF_00116
InterPro - IPR008180, IPR008181

Columns.Name: DatabaseUrl
Columns.Description: The URL of the database location for the associated entry.
